subsection.text:

            Subpart 1 of part C of title IV of the
			 Public Health Service Act (
              42 U.S.C. 285 et seq.
            ) is amended by adding at the
			 end the following:

clause.text:
needs and outcomes
				of pediatric cancer survivors within minority or other medically underserved
				populations;

health
				disparities in pediatric cancer survivorship outcomes within minority or other
				medically underserved populations;

subparagraph.text:
the development of
				indicators used for long-term patient tracking and analysis of the late effects
				of cancer treatment for pediatric cancer survivors;
